Default docking button factory implementation.

Optional UI-properties:

  • JYDocking.titlebar[.active].minimizeButton.icon [.disabled | .pressed | .hover][.selected] - String, Icon path or className
  • JYDocking.titlebar.minimizeButton.insets - Insets, specifies empty border size, default is 0 0 0 0
  • JYDocking.titlebar[.active].maximizeButton.icon [.disabled | .pressed | .hover][.selected] - String, Icon path or className
  • JYDocking.titlebar.maximizeButton.insets - Insets, specifies empty border size, default is 0 0 0 0
  • JYDocking.titlebar[.active].floatButton.icon [.disabled | .pressed | .hover][.selected] - String, Icon path or className
  • JYDocking.titlebar.floatButton.insets - Insets, specifies empty border size, default is 0 0 0 0
  • JYDocking.titlebar[.active].closeButton.icon [.disabled | .pressed | .hover] - String, Icon path or className
  • JYDocking.titlebar.closeButton.insets - Insets, specifies empty border size, default is 0 0 0 0
